```java
class Solution {
    public void sortColors(int[] nums) {
        int[] counts = new int[3];
        for(int num: nums) {
            counts[num]++;
        }

        for(int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if(counts[0] > 0) {
                nums[i] = 0;
                counts[0]--;
                continue;
            }
            else if(counts[1] > 0) {
                nums[i] = 1;
                counts[1]--;
                continue;
            }else if(counts[2] > 0) {
                nums[i] = 2;
                counts[2]--;
                continue;
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## ÊîπÈÄ†ÁöÑcountsum

```java
class Solution {
    public void sortColors(int[] nums) {
        int n0 = -1, n1 = -1, n2 = -1;//‰∏â‰∏™Êï∞ÁöÑindex
        for(int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if(nums[i] == 0) {//ÂΩìÊòØ0ÊòØ‰∏â‰∏™Êï∞ÈÉΩÂæÄÂêéÂÜô
                nums[++n2] = 2;
                nums[++n1] = 1;
                nums[++n0] = 0;
            }else if(nums[i] == 1) {
                nums[++n2] = 2;
                nums[++n1] = 1;
            }else{//ÂΩìÊòØ‰∫åÁöÑÊó∂ÂÄôÔºåÂè™Ë¶Å2ÂæÄÂêéÂÜôÂ∞±ÂèØ‰ª•
                nums[++n2] = 2;
